{"tid":1660160,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"請推薦一啲日文文法書","createTime":"2019-10-17T10:50:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T06:35:13.000Z","uid":148659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8af0b8039765ff0c1fc2ba5e7b47ea483582e7e4","tid":1660160,"uid":148659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T10:50:54.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以推薦下日文文法書？<br />\n我想買一本包含N5-N1嘅文法，而且內容同解釋想要係全日文，去咗sogo睇過，啲書全部包實晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果上樂天或日本網會唔會訂到？<br />\n<br />\n嚟緊12月考N1，做pastpaper時想查文法，但係N1至N5分開咗5本，又要逐本查，而且啲文法又唔齊<br />\n<br />\n麻煩巴打絲打請出招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55676cb4f5ae5b659ea941ba87c32c51e8e5a2b7","tid":1660160,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T10:51:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Yk6szE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Yk6szE.jpg&h=f0e63ff5&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"e85f08ea3b3dfa268439404684420caddd0f00ca","tid":1660160,"uid":8435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T16:17:03.000Z","msg":"呢本日文文法辭典<br />\n基本上有齊晒能力試考試範圍嘅嘢<br />\n唔知香港有無日文版賣<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.jp/日本語文型辞典-グループジャマシイ/dp/4874241549/ref=mp_s_a_1_7?_encoding=UTF8&amp;imageClass=hi-res&amp;keywords=日本語+文法&amp;phoneCarrier=wifi&amp;phoneType=iPhone&amp;qid=1571328513&amp;rd=1&amp;s=books&amp;sr=1-7&amp;view=Touch9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.co.jp%2F%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E8%AA%9E%E6%96%87%E5%9E%8B%E8%BE%9E%E5%85%B8-%E3%82%B0%E3%83%AB%E3%83%BC%E3%83%97%E3%82%B8%E3%83%A3%E3%83%9E%E3%82%B7%E3%82%A4%2Fdp%2F4874241549%2Fref%3Dmp_s_a_1_7%3F_encoding%3DUTF8%26imageClass%3Dhi-res%26keywords%3D%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E8%AA%9E%2B%E6%96%87%E6%B3%95%26phoneCarrier%3Dwifi%26phoneType%3DiPhone%26qid%3D1571328513%26rd%3D1%26s%3Dbooks%26sr%3D1-7%26view%3DTouch9&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAWA